---
import "/src/styles/global.css";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutMe from "/src/assets/images/about_me.jpg";
const pageTitle = "About Me";
let style = "\
    position: absolute;\
    top: 0;\
    bottom: 0;\
    margin: 0;\
    height: 100%;\
    width: 100%;\
    object-fit: cover;\
    z-index: -1;\
"
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <title>{pageTitle}</title>
        <style>
            h1 {
                line-height: 0.9;
                margin-right: 3%;
                margin-top: 3%;
                font-size: 10vh;
                color: black;
                text-align: end;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 3vh;
                font-family: "JetBrains";
                padding: 10px;
            }
            .content {
                margin-top: 1vh;
                margin-left: 3%;
                margin-right: 3%;
                text-align: end;
                background-color: rgba(217, 217, 217, 0.5);
            }
            .credits {
                margin-top: 0px;
                margin-left: 50px;
                margin-right: 50px;
                background-color: rgba(217, 217, 217, 0.5);
                width: fit-content;

                p {
                    width: fit-content;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
        <Image
            src={aboutMe}
            style={style}
            alt="Foto of me"
            quality=100
            loading="lazy"
        />

        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <div class="content">
            <p>
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                Praesent a mi vel orci porta congue vitae sit amet enim.
                Phasellus non dui eget mauris ornare pretium. Ut laoreet posuere
                augue vel fringilla. Vestibulum vel tortor et dolor dictum
                pretium sit amet vel elit. Sed a porta arcu. Nullam vitae
                sagittis odio. Fusce tristique fermentum purus, a auctor metus
                varius vitae.
            </p>
            <p>
                Sed aliquet, libero id pharetra cursus, felis turpis ultricies
                urna, eget pretium lacus nulla at mauris. Cras sed ex faucibus,
                efficitur sapien id, pellentesque magna. In hac habitasse platea
                dictumst. Quisque non urna nec dui condimentum feugiat sit amet
                lacinia metus. Aenean vehicula nibh commodo tortor elementum
                ultricies. Maecenas nibh quam, rhoncus eu tempus vel, egestas
                vitae odio. Donec ac enim ut lectus ornare ullamcorper et id
                neque. Etiam eu sem nec mi pulvinar pretium vitae id purus.
                Donec et erat sed ante blandit elementum nec ac nunc. Integer
                convallis enim laoreet molestie placerat. Etiam porttitor
                pellentesque suscipit.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="credits">
            <p>Foto by: Elias Bergman</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
